Discover this unique city, several times winner of the award &quot;City with the world&#39;s best quality of life&quot; and see its different faces. During the journey you will pass by the &quot;Must see&quot; of the beautiful town.

Departure point:&nbsp;
Sihlquai Coach Parking -&nbsp;Bus parking near Main Station.
www.switzerland-tours.ch/travelinfos

Check-In:&nbsp;
Please check-in at our ticket office marked with &quot;Best of Switzerland Tours&quot; at the latest 15 minutes prior to departure.
